Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.51,0:01:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Green Green
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hananoka Foundation Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.30,0:01:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, they're coming tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.63,0:01:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean those experimental transfer\Nstudents from Kanenone Gakuen?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.30,0:01:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder whet kind of guys they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.10,0:01:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if they're cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.81,0:01:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well since they're from the mountains,\Nthey're probably just monkeys...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.68,0:01:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She has a point...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.73,0:01:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on... Where did everyone go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.94,0:01:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.78,0:02:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling sick or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.66,0:02:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's all right... I was just a little... surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.29,0:02:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If I just take my medication...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.58,0:02:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.26,0:02:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's a ghost house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.13,0:02:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanae-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.13,0:02:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to spill it, I'm going to spill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.10,0:02:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanae-chan just wait a little longer, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.94,0:02:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.86,0:02:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be much faster if I carry her there\Ninstead of you bringing the water here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.61,0:02:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the drinking fountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.53,0:02:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A-ah, over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.41,0:02:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I see crows live in cities like this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Crows have a tendency to collect shiny\Nthings. Be sure to get a good look!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,– W-what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.05,0:02:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:03:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Armbadge - public morals committee
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.72,0:03:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So Haruno-san liked these kinds of things...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.14,0:03:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that, Futaba-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.18,0:03:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way that's true, right? How disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.40,0:03:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wakaba?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes, Onee-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, there's always one each year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,One of those bastards who use the darkness\Nto try and hug one of our student girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.29,0:03:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll eat you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No use in doing that, I'm not seared at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no such thing as a real ghost, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumbass! What are you touching?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ghost House
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:03:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.86,0:04:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot, it must have been hard on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're thirsty, right? After sweating like that and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? No, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.63,0:04:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, umm... I'm Chitose Midori.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.17,0:04:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Takasaki Yuusuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave these here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Bacchigu and Ichibanboshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I have to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.81,0:04:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I said wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.03,0:04:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Socho! Itsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Dokugasu's name, which is presumably\Na nick name of some kind, means "Poison Gas"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenjin! Dokugasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,H-help us!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.08,0:04:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch those guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.63,0:04:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They're perverts!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.54,0:05:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He touched my breasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,AFFEC-TION!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Bacchigu... Ichibanboshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And for those reasons, during the upcoming week,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll be studying side-by-side with the\Nmale students from Kanenone Gakuen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is also a test for us to see if we'll\Nbecome a co-ed school in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be anticipating everyone to be the neat and\Ndignified Hananoka Gakuen students that we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.55,0:05:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh! What part of this is "neat and dignified"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,W-what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys haven't been forgiven yet, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just staying quiet because a regent\Nsenpai punished you instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The next time you pull off one of your\Ndirty pranks, I'll notify the teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.69,0:06:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and get you guys kicked out right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}No guys allowed past this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, a bunk bed, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We slept on the floor at Kanenone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.96,0:06:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is heaven compared to that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The blanket's not wet, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how many years it's been\Nsince I've slept in a bed like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenjin... aren't those Bacchigu and Ichibanboshi's bags?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two left their bags to me and went out for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They went out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They said they were going to go exploring or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Exploring?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I get the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Takasaki Yuusuke-kun here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ass! Ass! Ass! Ass! Ass! Ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.89,0:07:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys are the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.19,0:07:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}No entry
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, it's nothing to be thanked for...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my type of girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, we came thinking that we'd show\Nyou around the school in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.33,0:07:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.75,0:07:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like we've got off on a bad start\Nbecause of yesterday's "incident", so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.05,0:07:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.01,0:07:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuusuke! Don't tell me you're leaving me behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:08:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you know when the same commercials appear???\Non different TV channels at the same time anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.93,0:08:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, my bestest friend in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,– Geez, you're noisy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it all right if he tags along, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Itsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tenjin, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.12,0:08:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can just smell the youth in the air...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There are so many women in the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Socho...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have any special talents, Yuusuke-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Like judo, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we have that as a class back at our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What in the world is she thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.71,0:09:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Chitose-senpai, will this really be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.88,0:09:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuusuke! Be sure to teach her a lesson\Nthat'll make her fear us men!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We even cheered him on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.35,0:09:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not supposed to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If you won, everyone would have a better impression\Nof you like Hotta-senpai outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.86,0:09:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So were you distracted by your opponent's\Nbreasts by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.28,0:09:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,T-that's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.79,0:09:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanae-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about that girl who's as tall as a junior\Nhigh student, but looks like she's in elementary school?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really, really genuine, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment you set your eyes on my girl, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When will we be able to decorate the\Nfirst page of the morning paper...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to wait every morning in excitement!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty dangerous, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the fragrance of a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Itsuki catch a cold or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,– Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, we've never taken\Na bath together with Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Until just a while ago, girls were in this very place!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty delicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:10:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a girlfriend at the\Nschool you were attending?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.08,0:11:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of girls do you like, Kobayashi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.08,0:11:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl who doesn't talk a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.17,0:11:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that Itsuki {\i1}is{\i0} quite handsome...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Socho would be in karate...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenjin would be with that freshman chick...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you're pretty knowledgeable\Nabout those things, Kuyasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then do you know about White Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.14,0:11:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Dokugasu is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about us?! I won't allow that kind of thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.90,0:11:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know... You're just reaping what you sowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that it's my fault? Aren't we friends?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to our friendship? Huh? Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well don't get so mad about\Nit... Yuusuke's right and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Bacchigu, did you apologize to that Haruno girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.51,0:12:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A-all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My fellow female comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's wash away what happened back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's all be friendly... Are you happy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.11,0:12:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wash {\i1}you{\i0} away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.94,0:12:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to reflect over what you've done more!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Reflect over it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.03,0:12:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.66,0:12:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Retard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Just die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You old pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Useless bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuusuke-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi... Chitose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Ijuin-kun... Ichibanboshi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.01,0:12:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Who does she mean by "Ijuin"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.63,0:12:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there a guy like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.80,0:12:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She's talking about me! Why did you forget?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! A pervert like you doesn't deserve that name!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.68,0:12:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to take this on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.93,0:12:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.81,0:12:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, Futaba-chan, Ijuin-kun,\Nlet's get along, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Midori-chan, there's no way we can\Nget along with these kind of guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.99,0:13:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "these kind of guys"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They seem pretty nice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.87,0:13:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's "pretty nice" about guys\Nwho do perverted things?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Futaba-chan, back then we were just...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.92,0:13:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We were joking around a little too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And we are really... sorry for it, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Pervert! Don't come...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,closer to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Futaba-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.36,0:13:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It... swelled up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.19,0:13:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He's an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Socho's not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys... What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think of Chitose Midori?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.84,0:14:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl came from a different\Nclass just to talk to us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If I explain up to here, even you\Nwould understand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.23,0:14:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She has a crush...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! You really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,On me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.44,0:14:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A man can't just stand and watch as he's being tempted!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Although this kind of thing isn't\Nreally my hobby at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichibanboshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We only have one day left anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make that headstrong girl fall for\Nme and call me "Ichibanboshi-sama"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.92,0:14:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,H-hey! I don't get what you guys are talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,– I'm going to become a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In conclusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They're nightcrawling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.60,0:14:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nightcrawling?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Chitose... Chitose's in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:14:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave them alone. There's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,B-but...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way they wouldn't have any kind of\Nsecurity around a girl's dormitory, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.82,0:15:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Security?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.11,0:15:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.95,0:15:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, mom, how are you? We're in the city right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The city is really a scary place. They looked\Ndown on us again thanks to Ichibanboshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.66,0:15:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, it's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's definitely your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,W-w-what did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.05,0:15:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I said we're being framed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, Yuusuke, we were at the dorm, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.55,0:15:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He's lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.97,0:15:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all saying that we're the criminals\Nin yesterday's incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but do you have any evidence... Futaba-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.32,0:15:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you get those cuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,T-these are... from that time when we\Nfell while being chased by wild dogs...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.87,0:15:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,R-right, Yuusuke? They were really big, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:15:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and confess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're full of lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.67,0:16:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll right, all right, that'll be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Just by what I've heard, there seems to be no evidence\Nthat the guys are indeed the criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.34,0:16:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, we were framed... I'm hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.01,0:16:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There's blood coming out from my wounds, mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.31,0:16:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I've lived without telling a single lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, what part of me is wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, am I a bad boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Mama...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.03,0:16:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What a disaster! They said Chitose Midori-san\Ngot her underwear stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,W-wait, we never did such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah... We never had time to do such a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.62,0:16:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So it {\i1}was{\i0} you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's been decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.46,0:16:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys will just have to get out right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back to the countryside!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.80,0:16:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, come on... Hold on, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.84,0:16:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to talk like that,\NI guess we have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.39,0:16:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're going to get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.51,0:17:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't just simply get out after getting\Naccused of being underwear thieves!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.68,0:17:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just have to catch the thief by\Nourselves and prove our innocence!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch him? But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.11,0:17:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Yuusuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.44,0:17:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Why do I have to do it, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez... Why do we have to it, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you standing guard properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.67,0:17:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my special talent and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.93,0:17:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But the city sure is hot at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.81,0:17:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Really... I should really be sleeping in\Na nice air-conditioned room by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.56,0:17:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose fault do you think this is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.11,0:17:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we're standing guard, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, be thankful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.86,0:17:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You got us into this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:18:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's so hot, I can't stop sweating.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuusuke, handkerchief...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, handkerchief...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, here's one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.34,0:18:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But do you really intend on catching the criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.38,0:18:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going back tomorrow, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if we don't catch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The real culprit will be caught before then, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"Oh, we've done something bad to Ijuin-kun."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.23,0:18:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,"That's right, let's write a letter!"\NSomething like that will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! What a brilliant plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, a criminal that actually did\Nthis kind of thing is usually sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.86,0:18:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't even suppress his own desires, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It might just be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.74,0:18:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say things that even demons would laugh at!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.91,0:18:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a trap right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.79,0:18:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Say that earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition to that, there's also a pit full of\Ntacks just a little bit further to the side...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.59,0:18:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to kill someone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.98,0:19:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry... Just because my panties...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,N-no, I'm just trying to clear my name, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.48,0:19:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuusuke-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.82,0:19:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.74,0:19:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just confess. I'll keep it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.03,0:19:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The nightcrawler in my room... was actually {\i1}you{\i0}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.04,0:19:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It was also you who stole my panties, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you're mistaken! It really wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.25,0:19:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What...? So it really is like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.88,0:19:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.68,0:19:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you being so kind to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.02,0:19:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not exactly being kind to you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.27,0:19:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, you're really dull, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.90,0:19:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly... Question Number\NOne, would it be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.61,0:20:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.57,0:20:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you cover up for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.32,0:20:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I did? When?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well when we first met, at the nurse's office...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I spilled the water on your shirt,\Nbut you didn't tell sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I didn't really have a particular reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.71,0:20:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't have one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.13,0:20:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, if I say that I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.13,0:20:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.06,0:20:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what it'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.89,0:20:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Question Number Two. Why are you asking about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.81,0:20:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? W-well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I say... No particular reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.07,0:20:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.95,0:20:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This origami's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.99,0:20:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.54,0:20:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen this many stars before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I never really had the chance to watch\Nthe star-filled sky like this, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:21:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many more stars than that, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.42,0:21:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.59,0:21:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,More?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.88,0:21:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. My school's in the countryside, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.10,0:21:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The air is clean, so even the same stars shine brighter,\Nand the sky has many more stars than this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.06,0:21:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And even on a moonless night, you can tell the\Nshape of the mountain just by the starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.53,0:21:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see a starry sky like that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.61,0:21:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuusuke-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.32,0:21:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Question Number Three... Can I come\Nover to your house next time?
